==Highest major summits==
{{GeoGroup|section=Highest major summits}}
Of the highest major summits of Idaho, ten peaks exceed {{convert|3500|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} elevation and 34 peaks exceed {{convert|3000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} elevation.
